ws/mgm-buys-ridley-scotts-gucci-film-lady-gaga-set-star-1289108? MGM Buys Ridley Scott's 'Gucci' Film With Lady Gaga Set to Star (Exclusive)]</ref></center>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"7\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#87f7bf; textcolor:#000;\" |D<br>E<br>C<br>E<br>M<br>B<br>E<br>R\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| 17\n|| ''[[Avatar 2]]'' || [[20th Century Studios]] || [[James Cameron]] (director/screenplay); [[Josh Friedman]] (screenplay); [[Sam Worthington]], [[Zoe Saldana]], [[Stephen Lang]], [[Sigourney Weaver]], [[Giovanni Ribisi]], [[Joel David Moore]], [[Dileep Rao]], [[CCH Pounder]], [[Matt Gerald]], [[Kate Winslet]], [[Cliff Curtis]], [[Michelle Yeoh]], [[Jemaine Clement]], [[David Thewlis]], [[Vin Diesel]] ||<center><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/854041-joel-david-moore-to-reprise-his-role-for-the-avatar-sequels#/slide/1|title=Joel David Moore to Reprise His Role for the Avatar Sequels|date=31 May 2017|publisher=Comingsoon|accessdate=31 May 2017}}</ref></center>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center\"| 21\n| ''[[Hotel Transylvania (franchise)#Hotel Transylvania 4 (2021)|Hotel Transylvania 4]]'' || [[Columbia Pictures]] / [[Sony Pictures Animation]] || [[Michael McCullers]] (screenplay); [[Adam Sandler]], [[Andy Samberg]], [[Selena Gomez]], [[Kevin James]], [[Fran Drescher]], [[Steve Buscemi]], [[Molly Shannon]], [[Keegan-Michael Key]], [[David Spade]], [[Adam Sandler#Personal life|Sadie Sandler]], [[Asher Blinkoff]], [[Mel Brooks]], [[Kathryn Hahn]] ||<center><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/02/hotel-transylvania-4-christmas-2021-1202565733/|title='Hotel Transylvania 4' To Open Doors Christmas Season 2021|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|date=February 26, 2019|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=February 26, 2019}}</ref></center>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center\" | 22\n| ''[[DC Extended Universe#Black Adam (2021)|Black Adam]]'' || [[Warner Bros.|Warner Bros. Pictures]] / [[New Line Cinema]] / [[DC Films]