riete Onaodowan]], [[Anthony Ramos (actor)|Anthony Ramos]] ||<center><ref>{{cite web|title=JUST ANNOUNCED: Disney Bringing Hamilton Movie with Original Broadway Cast to Theaters|url=https://d23.com/disney-bringing-hamilton-movie-with-original-broadway-cast-to-theaters/|website=Disney D23|date=3 February 2020}}</ref></center>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center\"| 22\n| ''[[The Addams Family (2019 film)#Sequel|The Addams Family 2]]'' || [[Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer]] / [[Universal Pictures]] || [[Conrad Vernon]], [[Greg Tiernan]] (directors); [[Oscar Isaac]], [[Charlize Theron]], [[Chlo\u00eb Grace Moretz]], [[Finn Wolfhard]], [[Nick Kroll]], [[Snoop Dogg]], [[Bette Midler]], [[Allison Janney]]||<center><ref name=\"Deadlinesequel\">{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/addams-family-2-in-works-fall-2021-release-1202760482/|title='The Addams Family 2' Is In The Works After Great $35M+ 4-Day Weekend, MGM/UAR Set Fall 2021 Release|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|last2=D'Alessandro|first2=Anthony|date=2019-10-15|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2019-10-15}}</ref></center>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#bf87f7; textcolor:#000;\" |N<br>O<br>V<br>E<br>M<br>B<br>E<br>R\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"| 5\n| ''[[Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness]]'' || [[Marvel Studios]] || [[Sam Raimi]] (director); Jade Bartlett and Michael Waldron (screenplay)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/doctor-strange-2-director-drops-out|title=Doctor Strange 2 Director Drops Out|first=Matt|last=Kim|publisher=[[IGN]]|date=January 9, 2020|accessdate=January 9, 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"WaldronDS2\">{{cite web|url=https://collider.com/doctor-strange-2-michael-waldron-rewrite-script/|title=\u2018Doctor Strange 2\u2019 Taps \u2018Loki\u2019 Scribe Michael Waldron to Rewrite Script|last=Sneider|first=Jeff|work=[[Collider (website)|Collider]]|date=February 7, 2020|accessdate=February 21, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org